sentences: Jarkko Kalevi Ahola  (born 24 August 1977, in Toijala) is a performing artist, a composer and a singer.
In 2013 took part in the project Forces United, where he acted in the role of vocalist.

He is also a member of a Finnish symphonic metal cover supergroup Northern Kings together with Marko Hietala from Nightwish, Tarot and Sapattivuosi, Tony Kakko from Sonata Arctica and Juha-Pekka Lepp√§luoto from Charon and Harmaja.
In addition, Jarkko has taken part in the Raskasta Joulua project incorporating the sound of metal to Christmas carols.
